## Limitations

This report is based on available data and news articles up to October 2023. The dynamic nature of geopolitical events and market conditions means that the situation can change rapidly, potentially affecting oil prices in unforeseen ways. Additionally, the analysis is limited to publicly available information and may not capture all factors influencing oil prices.